Glyphs are taken from "Lohit Bengali" made by Automatic Control Equipments,
Pune, INDIA.

Font adapted to UNICODE by the contributors of www.ekushey.org

TrueType hintings have been added by Alamigr Mohammed (alamgir99@gmail.com) and
Ershadul Haq (ershad@gmail.com).

